  "html_url": "https://github.com/srinitude/pi-until-done",
  "description": "A Pi extension command that executes raw user intent to completion with strict, verifiable termination. `/until-done` runs until a truthful terminal state: 1) all criteria are objectively satisfied or 2) cannot proceed safely, deterministically, or verifiably. It never stops based on perceived completion or invents success.",
